---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="Homelab & Uses — nbdevlab" description="Hardware, software, and services powering the nbdevlab homelab.">
  <section aria-labelledby="uses-title">
    <h1 id="uses-title">Homelab &amp; Uses</h1>
    <p>The nbdevlab rack is a rotating collection of gear, but these are the staples that stay powered on and patched.</p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="hardware-title" class="mt-10">
    <h2 id="hardware-title">Core hardware</h2>
    <ul class="uses-list">
      <li>
        <h3>Compute</h3>
        <p>
          Proxmox VE cluster running on a pair of HP ProLiant DL360 Gen9 nodes with dual Xeon E5-2680v4 CPUs, 128&nbsp;GB ECC RAM,
          and mirrored NVMe boot drives. GPU passthrough to an RTX 4000 for AI workloads.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Storage</h3>
        <p>
          TrueNAS SCALE with 6×12&nbsp;TB drives in RAID-Z2, plus a fast NVMe cache pool. Backups replicate to a Wasabi bucket nightly.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Networking</h3>
        <p>
          pfSense gateway with dual WAN failover, UniFi aggregation switch, and a Wi-Fi 7 AP covering the lab and office.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="software-title" class="mt-12">
    <h2 id="software-title">Favorite tooling</h2>
    <ul class="uses-list">
      <li>
        <h3>Observability</h3>
        <p>Grafana, Loki, and Tempo pipelines with k6 for synthetic checks and Uptime Kuma for quick pings.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Developer workflow</h3>
        <p>Astro, Cloudflare Pages, GitHub Actions, and task runners scripted with npm and justfiles.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Automation</h3>
        <p>n8n for event-driven flows, Ansible for patch windows, and Cloudflare Workers for edge-side glue.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <style>
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 2.6vw + 1rem, 3.2rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      max-width: 60ch;
    }
    .uses-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .uses-list h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .uses-list p {
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</SiteLayout>
